Stogas modifications:

- `core/` contains the imported Bifrost runtime/provider code. Stogas changes to
  this directory are gateway-runtime changes only: provider compatibility,
  request/response behavior, tests, and the minimal adjustments needed by the
  Stogas public API gateway.
- `transports/` contains the Stogas public gateway transport, catalog routing,
  confidential proof/provisioning code, and runtime entrypoints.
- `stogas/` contains Stogas release tooling, catalog tooling, and deterministic
  SEV-SNP IGVM build inputs.
- `.github/` contains Stogas-owned CI and release workflows.

Upstream Bifrost application, deployment, and non-runtime artifacts are not part
of this public runtime fork and are unused by Stogas Gateway.
